Cookies and Log-Files
I agree that Songs of Jesus Ministry Appuses cookies as follows:
Songs of Jesus Ministry Appuses cookies to store visitors’ preferences, record session information, record user-specific information on what pages users access or visit, record past activity at a site in order to provide better service when visitors return to our site, customize Web page content based on visitors' browser type or other information that the visitor sends.
Cookies are text files that are either temporarily stored in the random access memory or on the hard drive of your computer. They generally serve for offering the User the services of Songs of Jesus Ministry App with the User’s personal settings in each new session. Cookies are partly stored permanently on the User’s hard drive. The User may prevent this by setting his/her browser accordingly.
